brltty|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
brltty: brltty (Braille display driver for Linux/Unix)
brltty:
brltty: BRLTTY is a background process (daemon) which provides access to the
brltty: Linux/Unix console (when in text mode) for a blind person using a
brltty: refreshable braille display. It drives the braille display, and
brltty: provides complete screen review functionality.
brltty: Some speech capability has also been incorporated.
brltty:
brltty: http://mielke.cc/brltty/
brltty:
brltty: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
